Package: oncoCluster
Type: Package
Title: Identifies Cancer sub-types by using clustering algorithms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Shahzada Muhammad Shameel", "Farooq",
              email = "shahzada.farooq@mail.utoronto.ca",
              role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Shahzada Muhammad Shameel Farooq <shahzada.farooq@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: R package to identify cancer sub-types through the use of both 
    single and multi-omics data. The package employs various clustering 
    algorithms allowing the user to compare the results of the different 
    methods.
